Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.68,0:01:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.78,0:02:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的蛋糕又做壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.72,0:02:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴小姐，不要慌不要急\N冷靜一點，妳一定能成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要冷靜是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我最不拿手的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.44,0:02:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼少爺\N莓鈴小姐想為您做好吃的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.21,0:02:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是結果弄成這樣\N她的好意請您心領吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.99,0:02:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我會收拾乾淨的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.23,0:02:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.37,0:02:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，這裡是李家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.74,0:02:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是蛋糕嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.64,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裡面充滿了莓鈴小姐的愛心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.41,0:03:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直覺得\N您是一個心胸寬大的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.38,0:03:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過您好像對一些小事\N非常的介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不只是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.59,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她平常總是突然跑過來抱我\N小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.76,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟妳說過好多次\N不要突然衝過來抱我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.17,0:03:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.77,0:03:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想回去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.84,0:03:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第43話 再見了，莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍得真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.05,0:03:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是才藝會時哥哥幫我拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.32,0:03:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，妳哥哥好會拍照喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.59,0:03:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為照相機好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.43,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.47,0:04:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.81,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次演戲的照片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.42,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要回去了？\N什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會那麼突然…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,李同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.71,0:04:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要回香港的事\N有告訴老師了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要辦很多的手續\N得快一點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.69,0:04:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，我回香港你都無所謂嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.39,0:05:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊\N妳媽都叫妳回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.17,0:05:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼你嫌我煩嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.01,0:05:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我留在這裡會礙到你嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.72,0:05:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.66,0:05:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴要回去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.83,0:05:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事要告訴大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.73,0:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴同學下個星期\N要轉回香港的學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.64,0:05:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家會很寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.09,0:06:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜…\N再見…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.40,0:06:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要不要來我家住？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.95,0:06:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸烤了很好吃的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.06,0:06:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸很會做菜\N他煮的晚飯很好吃喔，而且…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且…\N我也想跟妳好好的聊天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.78,0:06:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.79,0:07:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起，我突然約了莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要突然約她？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.96,0:07:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很想找機會跟莓鈴聊天\N這是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.77,0:07:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且讓莓鈴沒跟你和好就回去\N她會很寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.81,0:07:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我去跟溫伯說一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.71,0:07:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪，到我家吃飯吧\N你一個人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了，老是打擾你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.75,0:07:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.32,0:07:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了\N打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.16,0:07:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻有客人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，聽說今晚要住在家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.13,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是知世嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，是第一次來的客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.80,0:07:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說是從香港來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香港？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃得好飽喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.21,0:08:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳爸爸真的很會做菜耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.62,0:08:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.15,0:08:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來\N謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.59,0:08:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，那個洗澡用的海綿呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可在知世家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.86,0:08:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的！臭丫頭到家裡住\N小櫻就把我趕出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.00,0:08:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來還想慢慢教導她\N人生是什麼東西呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.27,0:08:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有蛋糕吃\N還有我英勇的樣子可看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.94,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶而這樣也不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說真的，我實在太酷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.82,0:08:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是小櫻可以跟莓鈴好好聊聊\N那就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.56,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個好好吃喔\N這個也是，這也好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妳要減肥恐怕很辛苦喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.80,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好好吃\N我嘴巴都塞滿食物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.87,0:09:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,李…李同學也很會做菜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.82,0:09:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想李同學他絕對不會認為\N有妳在會礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.63,0:09:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為李同學他總是很擔心妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.27,0:09:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管在學校的時候\N或是蒐集牌的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.61,0:09:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩個？\N哪個才是真的啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.66,0:10:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.89,0:10:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那並不是我想要的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.74,0:10:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木之本妳為什麼會喜歡上那個人呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是哥哥的同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.35,0:10:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又常常來家裡玩，還有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.28,0:10:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳對他一見鍾情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.72,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴妳呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.76,0:11:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對小狼並不是一見鍾情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.43,0:11:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在香港\N我家離小狼家很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我沒有魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.24,0:11:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒有學習魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.47,0:11:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我跟小狼一起\N隨著溫伯學習武術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.23,0:11:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.46,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小狼從來不笑也不說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像現在那樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.84,0:11:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更嚴重\N我從來沒看他高興過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.98,0:12:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我對他很沒輒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.93,0:12:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的鳥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飛走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.57,0:12:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是阿姨給我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.04,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我最喜歡的鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.13,0:12:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼少爺，您要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去找鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.81,0:13:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他去找鳥了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.98,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來，下了大雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.45,0:13:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小狼還是沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.70,0:13:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.43,0:13:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您放心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.17,0:13:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼少爺一定會找到小鳥\N把牠帶回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.25,0:14:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這隻鳥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.89,0:14:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？哪裡痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.64,0:14:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來發生過這種事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.41,0:14:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在那以後吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.31,0:14:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.74,0:14:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是一起長大的\N所以我喜歡上他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.01,0:14:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小狼就不是那樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.49,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他曾跟我約定，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.66,0:14:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.59,0:15:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算跟他在一起\N也不能做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.23,0:15:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像找牌這件事，我也幫不上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.37,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛牌的氣息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.75,0:15:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，現在我朝著\N傳來庫洛牌氣息之處飛去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳換好衣服了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.15,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.19,0:15:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴，妳不去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.96,0:15:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.07,0:15:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美術館的作品全都變成兩個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.41,0:15:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是就算我去也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.32,0:16:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴，有很多事\N只有妳才辦得到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.60,0:16:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.97,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是「雙」牌（twin）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.27,0:16:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.41,0:16:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們家也變成兩個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼少爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連老伯也變成兩個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.69,0:16:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在搞什麼？好慢喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.79,0:16:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.13,0:16:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，你沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.83,0:16:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.30,0:16:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.84,0:16:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「跳」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風啊\N請捲起封鎖氣流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「風」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.80,0:17:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢復你原來的樣子，庫洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.81,0:17:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.21,0:17:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要抓雙牌\N只抓到一個是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.89,0:17:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要讓他們同時都不能動才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.73,0:17:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「跳」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.83,0:17:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要同時是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.70,0:17:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.87,0:18:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷帝召來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「雷」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一打暗號\N就會被他們發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.80,0:18:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定得同時攻擊才行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.03,0:18:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能完全同時攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.70,0:18:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算打了暗號也不可能同時啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.77,0:18:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再試一次看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.27,0:18:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，會成功嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是也只能試試看了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.52,0:18:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.45,0:18:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,李同學，你跟莓鈴的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.09,0:18:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定不必打暗號\N也能同時阻止他們的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木之本？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為莓鈴是跟小狼一起長大的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.54,0:19:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會…礙手礙腳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.81,0:19:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.89,0:19:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.25,0:20:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.69,0:20:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢復你原來的樣子，庫洛牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.31,0:20:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從來就不覺得妳礙手礙腳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦的臭丫頭回去了以後\N就一點都不好玩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.77,0:21:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會很寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.85,0:21:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有東西忘了帶吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.68,0:21:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去辦手續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了香港我會再跟您連絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.33,0:21:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎？那個約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.37,0:21:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,約定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.34,0:21:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡小狼\N我要當你的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.21,0:21:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.18,0:22:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狼，除了我以外\N你有更喜歡的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.48,0:22:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.52,0:22:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣，我就要當你的新娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.55,0:22:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.86,0:22:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.22,0:22:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有更喜歡的人\N我就死了這條心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.13,0:22:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是在那之前\N我是你的新娘喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.23,0:22:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.73,0:22:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.37,0:22:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.21,0:22:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便妳啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.78,0:22:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你找到你最喜歡的人以前\N我都是你的未婚妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.42,0:22:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.49,0:22:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴，我們還會再見面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.40,0:22:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了\N我一定會回到小狼的身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.87,0:22:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莓鈴小姐，時間到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.34,0:23:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.01,0:23:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N那個時候妳用魔法救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.85,0:23:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見，莓鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.77,0:24:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是雪兔哥\N參加弓箭大會的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.70,0:24:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都去幫他加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.70,0:24:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是小可卻突然不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.31,0:24:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.68,0:24:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？小可\N你怎麼會跟觀月老師在一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.18,0:24:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛魔法使\N「小櫻與小可與神秘的老師」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.69,0:24:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次也與小櫻一起\N解除封印！
